{"tid":1001163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯邦調查局（FBI）局長：幾乎所有經濟間諜案與中國有關","createTime":"2019-01-30T02:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T05:30:37.000Z","uid":13663,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e3cde311807d05fe73d4fe634fd7e73f5bd02ea3","tid":1001163,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:41:36.000Z","msg":"美國情報部門官員周二指中俄對美國構成最大威脅，指中俄關係是數十年來最密切，並可能已開始針對2020年美國總統選舉。<br />\n<br />\n國家情報總監科茨（Dan Coats）指中俄試圖擴大全球影響力，破壞昔日完善的安全規範，增加區域衝突的風險，尤其是中東與東亞地區。<br />\n<br />\n科茨指出，中、俄、伊朗、北韓越來越頻繁地利用網絡行動，以越來越多的方式威脅「思想與機器」：竊取資訊、影響美國公民、破壞重要基建。他指美國的敵人可能已試圖干預2020年美國選舉，他們的能力變得更強，也有了新技術。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦調查局（FBI）局長克里斯托弗‧雷（Christopher Wray）指中國構成最大的反情報威脅，指FBI手上的經濟間諜案，幾乎全部與中國有關。科茨則表示，情報官員走遍全美，與公司高層討論中國的間諜威脅。<br />\n<br />\n科茨又暗示，在中俄試圖擴大全球影響力之際，特朗普的安全與貿易政策令部份盟友棄美國而去。<br />\n<br />\n不過，科茨有幾項評估與總統特朗普的說法矛盾。科茨指北韓不大可能放棄核武，特朗普則指北韓不再構成威脅；科茨指「伊斯蘭國」（IS）會繼續在敍利亞伺機施襲，特朗普卻指IS已被擊敗，並計劃撤軍。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"803a68cf934187d5796155ea4f519a975a920035","tid":1001163,"uid":156936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國已成最大贏家"},{"pid":"6be1faa438c6aedb8492139255f95ffcc7e585b4","tid":1001163,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:09:49.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"9eaea78ea8c5f5c42970daace8d026f1dc8309b0","tid":1001163,"uid":200818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:12:21.000Z","msg":"嬴國又嬴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190c1b24ce30d3e8df0c108eba670d2bd4ff30b1","tid":1001163,"uid":61280,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:15:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">淨低就應該同香港有關！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"79c93b2ccffbb8e12c6f03544cb27584d5ea452f","tid":1001163,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63b82cc3d60fe76292c971579999dcd53416c32","tid":1001163,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:30:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}